{"tid":1456262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[極重要]係取消曬飛機航班後仲叫人留守好大機會係鬼，大家一定要mark低觀察","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T05:04:28.000Z","uid":119607,"like":74,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"7fcc5eba2ac640b61dc936382f122bd1b0306294","tid":1456262,"uid":119607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:55:22.000Z","msg":"LIHKG已被入侵得好嚴重，成場運動分分鐘因為咁而散，希望大家睇清D鬼。<br />\n<br />\n原因如下:<br />\n第一點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/12/XUflCh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F12%2FXUflCh.png&h=4a99458f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qn3FTMn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQn3FTMn.png&h=613b0770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1455153/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1455153/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>機管局取消起飛航班 (好明顯係有大事發生先會咁做)</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n另外唔少機場工作人員都出post話提早收工如:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1455097/page/1?post=2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1455097/page/1?post=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>呢D都係敵軍動靜，徹走D平民慢慢搞示威者。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n第二點<br />\n<br />\n今次機場集會本身大家共識係和理非，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>向旅客宣傳香港警察好危險，加上令警察濫暴上國際新聞，等外國投資者/政府覺得警察濫暴令香港動盪。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n依家旅客走曬，留守意義係咩? 叫人留守個班人答下我。<br />\n<br />\n第三點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>影響機場運作&lt;----今日目標達成<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n留守個班人可能問佔領唔係更好咩?<br />\n答:<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">現場大部份人都係冇Gear，係想班冇gear人同滿裝警察打?</span></strong>，上過前線巴打一定明有gear都危險，依家何況冇? 你想萬幾人送死? 仲叫人留守一定係警察臥底or食開人血饅頭ge冷氣軍師。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>我問多你地一樣野，一個半晝停飛嚴重D定每日停飛嚴重D，勝負唔係爭一日長短，be water共識都係咁得到。</strong><br />\n<br />\n第四點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所謂「三軍未動糧草先行」，想問一下留守ge人點樣解決糧食同物資? 機場條路一封就係咁先，留守佔領意義何在，今日係勢叫留守ge人一定冇上過前線。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最重要一點，舉旗先走，得一條路點走?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n第五點<br />\n<br />\n軍心，大部份集會ge人係冇心勇武，呢點唔係屌就屌得到D和理非慢慢勇武，好似前兩三日，前線都話冇豁出去ge心，幾多人都冇用。而且呢個時候屌人唔勇武同屌人用暴力都只係分化自己。<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為警察唔敢用武力，遊客一走，係機場就係非法集會，到時一定暴力清場，更甚可以用tear gar 迫曬D人入禁區，打做成恐怖份子。<span style=\"color: gold;\">要清場一個晚上都搞掂，最多都一日時間，而且仲要冇媒體可以採訪到，示威者處境更危險。</span><br />\n<br />\n到時候國際頭條就係警察鎮壓機場恐怖份子，credit比警察搶曬。 而唔係市民維權被鎮壓。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當然D人話咩拉曬示威者會上國際新聞，sorry，呢個戰略係「損敵一千，自損八百。」，出面ge人只係食緊人血饅頭。</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家仲記唔記得立法會一齊走，一齊走?唔解唔可以好好用呢次人數令每日機場運作減半?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n第六點<br />\n戰略意義/政治意義? 有冇支持留守ge人答下?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然今日走，聽日更難入，但係我唔支持被人一網打盡。留守付出後果更大。"},{"pid":"52880606711de0c910f88bc7d43932a8a25343e9","tid":1456262,"uid":119607,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:56:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要mark低咩人仲叫留守!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f301fc0f7619e5ee84b72a8cb82e2ff8230b18a6","tid":1456262,"uid":34088,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:56:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無航班無遊客 無遊客無宣傳</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">叫埋身邊人走 有車就上 走左先講</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有朋友係要現場就call爆佢叫佢走</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b613503c3cfb08e5af46edec3657044a263c1ea8","tid":1456262,"uid":23590,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:56:51.000Z","msg":"三張免費機鐵飛出青衣，qr code 一嘟出得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q0t27j1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ0t27j1.png&h=c811f2cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/12/175057_3bb32e981c2e4e4fa938eaeb37a158a7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F12%2F175057_3bb32e981c2e4e4fa938eaeb37a158a7.png&h=4839706d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZT2WsjZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZT2WsjZ.png&h=ad6e4ab4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"927762ed1673c96a4f4d879b771cee15f6d9575c","tid":1456262,"uid":287051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:56:53.000Z","msg":"走呀<br />\n一個都不能少"},{"pid":"6efaaf68cf6f201a841366657b8820dcb53bc3c1","tid":1456262,"uid":6845,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:57:15.000Z","msg":"抵港航班開返曬 好似係<a href=\"https://www.hongkongairport.com/tc/flights/arrivals/passenger.page\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongairport.com%2Ftc%2Fflights%2Farrivals%2Fpassenger.page&d=nSJvRvahoV7vX7tkwZxFzg5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=eba4c0db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongairport.com/tc/flights/arrivals/passenger.page</a>"},{"pid":"e3d8c20445186c59bd9e237f6ba40b12fd5d1bb1","tid":1456262,"uid":38472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:57:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcd82999fb63dbe892c45d457e29215bb6795814","tid":1456262,"uid":285516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:58:12.000Z","msg":"鬼嘅特點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">會用咩五大訴求嘅字眼引你留</span></span>"},{"pid":"611c95560024df547e3d4336c0db5d5a4764c3e3","tid":1456262,"uid":119607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6efaaf68cf6f201a841366657b8820dcb53bc3c1","tid":1456262,"uid":6845,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"r